{"tid":2082464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷李活將製作中國肺炎電影 大量支那人表示不滿","createTime":"2020-06-28T05:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T16:37:46.000Z","uid":231583,"like":887,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3deac5036b6014c0cd5900cfedf486aaa294d5","tid":2082464,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"蘋果全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200628/M6FPBBNUVR4AS3YJK3LF3DLXME/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0q9_x6v_jcQN3jerWA9Y8kvIsPhLoXreh3rlViK_ZUXEST5mYiTi1K030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200628%2FM6FPBBNUVR4AS3YJK3LF3DLXME%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0q9_x6v_jcQN3jerWA9Y8kvIsPhLoXreh3rlViK_ZUXEST5mYiTi1K030&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=6dc0901e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200628%2FM6FPBBNUVR4AS3YJK3LF3DLXME%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0q9_x6v_jcQN3jerWA9Y8kvIsPhLoXreh3rlViK_ZUXEST5mYiTi1K030&h=30f7c86e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200628/M6FPBBNUVR4AS3YJK3LF3DLXME/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0q9_x6v_jcQN3jerWA9Y8kvIsPhLoXreh3rlViK_ZUXEST5mYiTi1K030</a><br />\n<br />\n美國《華爾街日報》昨報道，曾製作《我的超豪男友》（Crazy Rich Asians）的荷李活公司SK Global Entertainment已聘請奧斯卡最佳編劇蘭道夫（Charles Randolph）拍攝一部反映武漢肺炎疫情在中國武漢爆發初期的醫療劇。蘭道夫說：「病毒如何從蝙蝠洞中落到武漢，這是一個我們不會很快就能解決的問題；這將更像是一部醫療劇，而不是關於瘟疫的驚慄片。」<br />\n<br />\n內地網民講乜：<br />\n宇未清源：醫療劇？怕是政治劇吧！<br />\n昵個貓昵：拍你們美國吧&hellip;&hellip;怎麼成為世界第一的，怎麼把美國肺炎說成電子煙肺炎的。<br />\n維羅尼卡2011：最大的蝙蝠應洞該是美國德特里里克堡生物驗室實，美國現在多少例（宗）了，不如關心一下自己國家的事。<br />\n火火857：我想拍一反映部美國我不能呼吸的電影！<br />\n大道當誅：美國人就這德行。自己國家一團糟，還要遺餘不力的抹黑別人。"},{"pid":"9685d929877c74a2d83eccdeb9b4e14bc163eab6","tid":2082464,"uid":231583,"like":489,"dislike":4,"score":485,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20150329/photo/bkncn-20150329232920876-0329_05011_001_01p.jpg?20150329233538\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20150329%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20150329232920876-0329_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20150329233538&h=f201125c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c94bf802e3375e67de2b7d09ec6bd93a40008b2","tid":2082464,"uid":231583,"like":243,"dislike":1,"score":242,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"一睇標題以為Hollywood拍電影幫中國洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實點解班支那人咁肯定套野一定係屌中國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定只要套野講肺炎係武漢開始=抹黑？"},{"pid":"9d363ebf4baa66aeb9fb2c1c5fd389e59dfbb5ac","tid":2082464,"uid":22675,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"咁快？！疫情未完喎，以為要等五年先有電影"},{"pid":"42840e9346f8f1a25b6d3e27372e6dc0a668cd81","tid":2082464,"uid":231583,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"9d363ebf4baa66aeb9fb2c1c5fd389e59dfbb5ac","tid":2082464,"uid":22675,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"咁快？！疫情未完喎，以為要等五年先有電影"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:11:22.000Z","msg":"拍定啱架啦，續集可以拍 支那收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39010b1f1aa0adc185b0714b3d4bd5eb23b0bd83","tid":2082464,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823c2469859e2fa0876023e19e1a77971b8fae60","tid":208246